sections.content: The property covered under Gift Settlement Deed No. 326 of 2026, dated 20/Jan/2026, executed by S Muragesh, in favour of his Wife, M Manjamma, towards the property admeasuring an extent of 117.11 Sq. Yds., located near by house number 3-20, comprised in survey number 293/1, situated in Ananthapuram Village, Kumbarlapalli Gramapanchayat, Venkatagirikota Mandal, within the District of Chittoor, registered at sub-registrar office Palamaner, is bounded as follows: North by: House of Rammurthy South by: Avula Shed of Paramesh East by: Road West by: House and Vacant Site of Amarana Note *Schedule property is part of Gramakantam as per recitals of the deed.
It is noted from the given documents and EC that the schedule property is not part of any active Mortgage or Lease Deed.

Note It is to be noted that the online EC has been verified using the key parameters, namely the Document Number, Survey Number/House Number of the concerned SRO, as per the Deed. However, cross-verification across multiple SROs has not been carried out due to the AP portal’s requirement of separate passwords for each search parameter, and the OTP-based authentication mechanism makes searches across multiple SROs operationally infeasible.
